high_descs: Begin across the room, then turn left and walk up to the green dresser.
Pick up the furthest pencil off of the dresser.
Turn right and begin walking to the wall, then hang a right and walk up to the wooden desk
Place the pencil on the desk a little ways to the left of the disc.
Turn around and walk back over to the green dresser.
Pick up the last pencil that is on the dresser.
Turn left and walk over to the wall, then turn right and walk up to the wooden dresser.
Place the pencil on the wooden desk a little ways to the left of the pencil that is already there.
anns.task_desc: Move two pencils to a wooden desk.

high_descs: Move to the low file cabinet.
Pick up the pencil, that is nearest the book, from the file cabinet.
Turn right, move to the desk near the chair.
Place the pencil on the desk, to the left of the CD.
Turn left and move to the low file cabinet.
Pick up the pencil on the low file cabinet.
Turn right, move to the desk near the chair.
Place the pencil on the desk left of the first pencil.
anns.task_desc: Place the pencils on the low file cabinet onto the desk.

high_descs: Go to face the green cabinet on your left.
Pick up the pencil that is farther from you.
Turn around and go to the desk behind you.
Put the pencil on the desk, pointing towards the center of the chair.
Turn around and return to the green cabinet behind you.
Pick up the remaining pencil from the cabinet top.
Carry the pencil back to the desk behind you.
Place the pencil on the desk, above the left arm of the chair, pointing toward the chair.
anns.task_desc: Move two pencils to a desk.

high_descs: Take two steps and turn left and walk forward to face a cabinet.
Pick up the top pencil on the table.
Turn to the right, walk across the room, turn to the right, walk across the room to face the table.
Place the pencil on the table.
Turn to the right, take a step, turn to the right walk across the room to face a cabinet.
Pick up the pencil laying on the cabinet.
Turn to the right, walk across the room, turn to the right, walk across the room to face the table.
Place the pencil on the table.
anns.task_desc: To move 2 pencils one at a time from a cabinet to a table.
